story.text: The question of interpretation is perhaps one of the most heated in the under the U.S. Constitution.

You should use the rest my fed.wiki pages to help discern my intention. But balance that with the generally available knowledge when this constitution is adopted - as I know that not everyone will have had the opportunity to study my thinking at length.
